metadata.name: Gemstones #01 -Skull
metadata.description:
This is my Artwork inpired in "Amethyst Gemstone".
Purple Stones have been adored for a long time, and for good reason. There's something about purple that intrigues people, and the color is often associated with royalty, wealth, passion, power, luxury, ambition and magic!
Diamonds are eternal and Bitcoins too.
Software: 3ds Max, ZBrush and FStorm Render.
Video in 1920 X 1080.
2K Video Loop.
